sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as Operator Controller Manager
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Engine
    participant ConfigMap as ConfigMap<br/>Feature Flags/Images
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Ingress as Ingress Controller<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Service as Llama Stack Service<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Pod as Llama Stack Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Provider as Inference Provider<br/>Ollama/vLLM
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    %% Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation
    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Provider: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation
        User->>K8sAPI: Create LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch notification<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount JWT
        Operator->>ConfigMap: Read feature flags & image overrides<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount JWT
        ConfigMap-->>Operator: Configuration data
        Operator->>Kustomize: Generate manifests<br/>In-process
        Kustomize-->>Operator: Deployment/Service/PVC/NetworkPolicy
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply resources<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount JWT
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources created
    end

    %% Flow 2: User Inference Request
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,Provider: Flow 2: User Inference Request (with Ingress)
        Client->>Ingress: POST /v1/models/llama:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Optional Auth
        Ingress->>Service: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8321 internal
        Service->>Pod: Route to pod<br/>HTTP/8321
        Pod->>Provider: Inference request<br/>HTTP/gRPC backend-specific
        Provider-->>Pod: Prediction result
        Pod-->>Service: Response
        Service-->>Ingress: Response
        Ingress-->>Client: JSON Response
    end

    %% Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Prometheus,Operator: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Proxy: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS<br/>Bearer Token
        Proxy->>K8sAPI: Validate token<br/>TokenReview/SubjectAccessReview
        K8sAPI-->>Proxy: Token valid
        Proxy->>Operator: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080 localhost
        Operator-->>Proxy: Metrics data
        Proxy-->>Prometheus: Metrics response
    end

    %% Flow 4: ConfigMap Update
    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 4: ConfigMap-driven Configuration Update
        User->>K8sAPI: Update ConfigMap<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS 1.2+<br/>User credentials
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch notification<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount JWT
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Reconcile LlamaStackDistributions<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount JWT
        K8sAPI->>Pod: Restart with new config<br/>Rolling update
    end
